pr_title: Fix Issue #53, #83: Predict possible species and gene ID
pr_body:
Fixes: #53, #83

New Task Created:
 - [OrganismAndGeneIdAssertionTask.java](https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/tasks/OrganismAndGeneIdAssertionTask.java)

Workflow:
1. While initialisation of `EnrichmentCytoPanel`, we call methods to set organism and gene ID.
https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/ui/EnrichmentCytoPanel.java#L271-L274
https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/ui/EnrichmentCytoPanel.java#L280-L281
 
2. In `setOrganism(final CyNetwork network)`:
   - First check if the organism is already present in the network, if present return.
   - Get list of all possible column that may contain species/organism information from [OrganismNetworkEntry Enum](https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/tasks/OrganismAndGeneIdAssertionTask.java#L102)
   - Iterate through values and check if any of the present values are also present in our list of organisms retrieved from GProfiler. Select the first value that matches.
   - Set the value in the network.

3. In `setGeneId(final CyNetwork network, final CyServiceRegistrar registrar)`:
    - First check if geneID is already present in network
    - If not, check network type and select appropriate column. Eg: [getGeneIdFromNetworkName](https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/tasks/OrganismAndGeneIdAssertionTask.java#L89)
    - If gene not found, get information from NODE_LABEL style.
    https://github.com/cytoscape/enrichment-table-app/blob/e216d18e6167c76520ecb51766842a15146a62b4/src/main/java/org/nrnb/gsoc/enrichment/tasks/OrganismAndGeneIdAssertionTask.java#L72-L78
